BREAKING CHANGE:

The model has moved from this:

```javascript
    {
      id: '1',
      element: 'function-entry',
      weight: 1,
      incorrectFeedback: {
        type: 'default',
      },
      correctResponse: {
        equation: '3x+2',
        feedback: {
          type: 'default',
        },
      },
      model: {
        showFormattingHelp: true
      }
    }

```

To this:

```javascript
    {
      id: '1',
      element: 'function-entry',
      weight: 1,
      showFormattingHelp: true,
      equation: '3x+2',
      feedback: {
        correct: {
          type: 'default',
          default: 'Correct'
        },
        incorrect: {
          type: 'default',
          default: 'Incorrect'
        }
      }
    }

```

